<A>__{close on a paint brush. it rests across the lid of a can of wood stain. see now... ...susan marie kneeling by the table she is refinishing. but her hands, her body, are motionless. her eyes stare out the window... ...across the yard. her towering husband walks beside a smaller man. carl is doing the talking. kabuo's face is stone.}
<L>__{interior parlor later}
<A>__{susan marie sits quietly in a rocker, nursing her baby. her hands tenderly stroke the feeding infant. but her eyes are attentive. concerned.}
